        "content": "<h3>3dCart is a hosted ecommerce platform that offers a wide variety of features, ranging from content management to store marketing and well beyond.</h3>\n\n<p>Platform upgrades allow for enhanced graphics and a revamped checkout experience for customers. The dashboard is intuitive and allows for full control over the store, even if its product listings go way over hundreds of products. If you have worked with Wordpress, 3dCart&#39;s dashboard will seem very familiar to you. The platform offers all kinds templates to help you create the unique look of your store, some of which are available for an additional fee. The great thing about this platform is that you are not limited to the drag and drop function for creating your front-end, but can also edit the code directly using HTML and CSS.&nbsp; There is also an app-store you can use to give your website features. The platform itself offers a lot of them, so you won&#39;t need to download multiple add-ons, meaning shorter response time for your website.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>3rdCart has some drawbacks. One of them being the limited amount of bandwidth that comes with each plan, making it sub-optimal for larger businesses and B2B companies.&nbsp;</p>\n",
